headline: Digital Wave Technology Expands Executive Team With Michael Henne, Chief Financial Officer and José Luis Sánchez Castro, Managing Director LATAM
summary: PONTE VEDRA, Fla., August 06, 2025--Digital Wave Technology, provider of the AI-native ONE℠ Platform powered by an AI-native Master Data Management foundation, today announced the appointments of Michael Henne as Chief Financial Officer (CFO) and José Luis Sánchez Castro as Managing Director for Latin America (LATAM). These strategic leadership additions further enhance Digital Wave’s ability to scale globally and deliver cutting-edge solutions to customers worldwide.
